Type: Package
Package: liuKoladaMini
Title: Minimal Kolada API Client for Municipalities, KPIs and Values
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Mohan", "Zhang", , "mohzh143@student.liu.se", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Minimal example package for Lab05. Provides three functions
    to access the Kolada API: list municipalities, list/search KPIs, and
    fetch KPI values for a municipality. Includes unit tests with recorded
    HTTP fixtures for offline replay.
